Would you swap bodies w/ someone for a day? #shortfilm #storytime 

I’ve been working on this piece for about six months. I’m so happy to be able to finally share this with y’all. I love my life most of the time. Regardless I’m still so curious to see how things feel in a different body. Do we see the same colors? Taste things the same? Move the same? I guess I’ll never know. If this resonates with you and you wanna support us consider sharing this on your IG story. 

Thanks to my amazing team for helping bring this vision to life. 
Choreography @ava_gordy 
Dancer @sierranarmstrong 
DP @kamdarfarhan 
Written, directed and edited by me
I steal from artists all the time #director #directors #shortfilm #howto #storytelling #cinematic #jimcarrey

I’m addicted to making money. I was raised this way. I randomly came across this video on my phone and felt like I should reshare it for all my new followers. Content like this typically struggles to find its audience because it isn’t made for the algorithm. So if you enjoy it plz consider engaging with this post. Maybe fuck around and add it to your IG story. But either way I hope you enjoy it. Maybe it resonates with you? Maybe you just like looking at a minority run. Idk. Anyways. I’m ready for my next creative idea to come to me. It hasn’t yet. But it will. 

Fun facts about this video:
1) I should’ve softened the edges of the binoculars. 
2) the final running shot is beautiful. 
3) I recorded this voice over a long time ago. I almost considered re recording the VO but I decided against it. Can I do it better now? Probably. But if I focus on always trying to make my work perfect I end up not making anything.

The winter time almost broke us up! #relationships #relationahip #podcast #goodtoseeya Hi this is Avalean reporting. The love we were shown from these short clips last year inspired a longer format visual podcast that we’ve just launched. I initially had some reservations because it’s a vulnerable thing- putting yourself out there. Saying things! According to a wise man, “Speak up. People want to hear you talk.” -daren🕺🏽 But the love y’all have shown us is real and we believe in that and it inspired us to do what we love. Have conversations where we would and show you glimpses of the life we are so blessed to live.
